_sText:
This is a relatively simple yet fun map. There are 2 floors and a basement. The first floor is separated into an array of 3 by 3; two of he side rooms connect into the center room. The second floor is a balcony overlooking the center room; the balcony and center room connect via ladders. Terrorists and CT start in opposite corners of of the map. In either spawn is a ladder leading to the low lit basement.

ENJOY!
